<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>F1 Streams & Discord</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b0b0b 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            color: #f5f5f5;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e10600, #ff6a00);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .invite-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #5865F2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .invite-btn:hover {
            background: #4752c4;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #ff6a00;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #ddd;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🏁 F1 Streams & Community</h1>
            <p>Every practice, qualifying, and race – live, free, and spoiler‑free</p>
            <a href="https://discord.gg/YOUR_INVITE_CODE" class="invite-btn" target="_blank">Join the Discord →</a>
        </header>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📺 Free Streams</h3>
                <p>Watch every F1 session live. No subscription, no ads – just the race.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🚫 No Spoilers</h3>
                <p>Our stage system hides channels until the session is live. Quali only during quali, race only during race.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🏎️ Team Roles</h3>
                <p>Pick your favourite constructor and show your colours. Ferrari, Mercedes, Red Bull, and more.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🗣️ Active Chat</h3>
                <p>Hang out in text or voice during the sessions. Memes, predictions, and good vibes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0;">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
            <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto;">
                Join the server, solve a quick math captcha to verify, pick your team role, and you're in.<br>
                During race weekends, only the current session's channel is visible – so you never get spoiled.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0;">
            <a href="https://discord.gg/YOUR_INVITE_CODE" class="invite-btn" target="_blank">Join the Grid →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>No paywalls, no spam. Just F1 with friends.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
